<title>INDIA: India Infosys announced 1-for-1 bonus.</title>
<headline>India Infosys announced 1-for-1 bonus.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-04-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The directors of software firm Infosys Technologies Ltd said on Tuesday it decided to issue bonus equity shares in the proportion of one share for every share held.</p>
</text>
